      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/cdc98d/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-02-26T10:44:01.465Z",
      "cooked": "<p>It\u2019s indeed very well possible it has something to do with my Garmin.  Because Garmin refuses to allow our favorite tool to upload activities in Garmin connect, I use a setup where Trainerday runs on my phone, controls the trainer and my Garmin is used for recording only.  Then the Garmin uploads the activity to Garmin Connect and Strava.  I will read the full topic later, but it\u2019s probably something to do with that indeed !</p>",
