      "name": "dermate",
      "username": "dermate",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ea666f/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-03-03T15:50:10.539Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes, if Garmin Edge kicks in too fast, TD loses the connection.</p>\n<p>So, my final \u201cofficial\u201d (ehm\u2026) workaround today is:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Power on your Direto</li>\n<li>Open TD app</li>\n<li>Wait for Direto and TD to connect via BLE (after a few seconds, you can actually hear DIreto hanshaking)</li>\n<li>Start a workout on TD</li>\n<li>Power on your Garmin Edge and wait it to connect to Direto via ANT+</li>\n<li>Start recording on Garmin Edge.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>There you go!</p>\n<p>Ciao</p>\n<p>Riccardo</p>",
